    <node id="Title">
      <data key="d0">Title</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The title of the research paper is "Personalized Worked Example Generation from Student Code Submissions using Pattern-based Knowledge Components".&lt;SEP&gt;The title of the research paper is "Benchmarking Source-Sensitive Reasoning in Turkish: Humans and LLMs under Evidential Trust Manipulation".&lt;SEP&gt;The title of the article is "Why AI Harms Can't Be Fixed One Identity at a Time: What 5300 Incident Reports Reveal About Intersectionality".&lt;SEP&gt;The title of the paper is "MIMIC: A Generative Multimodal Foundation Model for Biomolecules".&lt;SEP&gt;The title of the paper is "See Further, Think Deeper: Advancing VLM's Reasoning Ability with Low-level Visual Cues and Reflection".&lt;SEP&gt;The Title is the heading of the abstract, "RAS: a Reliability Oriented Metric for Automatic Speech Recognition".&lt;SEP&gt;The title of the paper is "Credal Concept Bottleneck Models for Epistemic-Aleatoric Uncertainty Decomposition".</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-421873c316a2a72fa1ccf5068ebdfe92&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c55766a45b0f180acb4d559b875dcdd9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-381164f8e5eeb1538b53d25d3cf781b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f03a6efec96a2141ce04fd7d8cd59d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee6a8292ee988e4d64c218b75e3c5f57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-245522d5b100e4d1a221b34fd4f3a20d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-186325b8d21aab395207850cb3577223</data>
