    <node id="Research Paper">
      <data key="d0">Research Paper</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">The research paper presents an approach for knowledge-component guided educational content generation using pattern-based knowledge components.&lt;SEP&gt;The research paper is a comprehensive study on source-sensitive reasoning in Turkish.&lt;SEP&gt;The research paper discusses the performance of continuous diffusion spoken language models.&lt;SEP&gt;The Research Paper is the document that presents the research findings and conclusions.</data>
