      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Transformer Architecture is a type of neural network architecture that dedicates enormous capacity to learning rich representations in semantic embedding space.&lt;SEP&gt;Transformer Architecture is a neural network design that inspired the development of SolarTformer.</data>
