      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Autonomous AI Agents are AI systems that can operate independently without human intervention.&lt;SEP&gt;Autonomous AI agents extend large language models into full runtime systems that load skills, ingest external content, maintain memory, plan multi-step actions, and invoke privileged tools.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-2c127bc04f3bde0cd314a75a26f2cec3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d66caa329c3a04aee4985803a47142b6</data>
