    <node id="Large Language Models (LLMs)">
      <data key="d0">Large Language Models (LLMs)</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Large Language Models (LLMs) are artificial intelligence models that perform strongly on general-purpose code generation.&lt;SEP&gt;Large Language Models are used in GraphRAG to generate answers.&lt;SEP&gt;Large Language Models (LLMs) are artificial intelligence models that can generate human-like text and have shown promise in code generation.&lt;SEP&gt;Large Language Models (LLMs) are artificial intelligence models that have shown strong capabilities in commonsense reasoning but struggle with diagnostic reasoning due to limited domain knowledge.&lt;SEP&gt;Large Language Models (LLMs) are machine learning models designed to process and generate human-like language.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ee26c6456033dbc512177b2b3161670e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64fad5be7471e063c4b5aa89695241f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-721cf18e9625b5e00d46286185f339e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0bcb21e87d929f93a36d3bdf947fcb93&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dce3b2b12a8df42087f6abb8d46338fb</data>
