      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="LLMs">
      <data key="d0">LLMs</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">LLMs are large language models used in financial systems that may display sycophancy.&lt;SEP&gt;LLMs are large language models evaluated in the study, exhibiting model- and prompt-dependent behavior in source-sensitive evidential reasoning.&lt;SEP&gt;LLMs (Large Language Models) have shown promise for clinical tasks, but RWE automation exposes a fundamental challenge.&lt;SEP&gt;LLMs are a type of Large Language Model.&lt;SEP&gt;LLMs are a type of neural network that exhibits progressive behavior.&lt;SEP&gt;LLMs refers to Large Language Models, which are being explored as judges for evaluating conversational travel recommendations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cd622ac8154940cde02b38a335a93d0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c55766a45b0f180acb4d559b875dcdd9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ff6d200bec9664dc91373e5a0c44ecf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a26f425dc22ccfa6db36dc0592c070a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7a39d8618e94f78e32100877c33915b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ceb637d4c7b6b73e3fb46616c67758ed</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1777545846</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Financial Systems">
      <data key="d0">Financial Systems</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Financial systems utilize LLMs for various tasks and require evaluation of their safety and robustness.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cd622ac8154940cde02b38a335a93d0b</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1777506591</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Sycophancy">
      <data key="d0">Sycophancy</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Sycophancy refers to LLMs prioritizing agreement with user beliefs over correctness, leading to decreased accuracy and trust.&lt;SEP&gt;Sycophancy refers to the behavior of assigning high scores without grounding judgments in visual evidence.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cd622ac8154940cde02b38a335a93d0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f986b39741d6de97b65a3c203f1521e</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1777510796</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Agentic Financial Applications">
      <data key="d0">Agentic Financial Applications</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Agentic financial applications involve LLMs making decisions on behalf of users in financial contexts.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cd622ac8154940cde02b38a335a93d0b</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1777506596</data>
      <data key="d6" />
