    <node id="Attention Latch">
      <data key="d0">Attention Latch</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The Attention Latch is a systemic failure mode in decoder-only autoregressive Transformers that causes agents to remain anchored to obsolete constraints.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fde07fa1707d44e8e8acbe99adf1542f</data>
