    <node id="Perceived Cooperativity Scale">
      <data key="d0">Perceived Cooperativity Scale</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The Perceived Cooperativity Scale is a theoretically grounded instrument for assessing the subjective quality of cooperative human-AI interaction, capturing an agent's perceived cooperative capability and practice within a single interaction sequence.</data>
