    <node id="Physics-Informed Neural Network (PINN)">
      <data key="d0">Physics-Informed Neural Network (PINN)</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">The Physics-Informed Neural Network (PINN) is a deep learning architecture used in the Deep Learning-Enabled Dissolved Oxygen Sensing paradigm to embed the Stern-Volmer (SV) equation into the loss function.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e755a3b7fb7a07c10fdd800c398a82c8</data>
