      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">AI safety refers to the development of methods and techniques to ensure that artificial intelligence systems behave in a safe and responsible manner, and is redefined by the Kerimov-Alekberli Model.&lt;SEP&gt;AI Safety refers to the development of methods and frameworks to ensure the safe and responsible deployment of artificial intelligence systems.</data>
